high_descs: Move to the bed on the left of you.
Close and pick up the laptop from the bed.
Move to the drawers to the right of you.
Place the laptop on the shelf above the drawers.
Move to opposite side of the bed behind you.
Pick up the other laptop from the bed.
Move to the drawers directly across from you.
Place the laptop near the other one on top of the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Move the laptops from the bed to the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the middle of the bed, and turn left towards the bed.
Close the lap top closest to you and pick it up from the bed.
Turn right and head towards the desk.
Place the lap top on the desk.
Turn around, head towards the middle of the bed, and turn left to face the bed.
Pick up the lap top on the bed.
Turn right and head towards the desk.
Place the lap top to the left of the other one on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place the two lap tops from the bed to the desk.

high_descs: Turn left and go forward until just before the rug, then turn left and go forward to the bed
Close and take the nearer laptop
turn right and cross the room to the cabinets
place the laptop on the counter above the cabinets
turn around and cross the room to the grey chairs, then turn right and go forward to the bedside table. Then, turn and face the bed.
Close and take the laptop on the bed
cross the room to the counter with the other laptop
place the laptop on the counter to the right of the other laptop
anns.task_desc: Move two laptops from the bed to the counter
